  "description": "A stunning sunset over a calm body of water. The sun, a bright, fiery orb, is positioned near the horizon, casting a long, shimmering reflection across the water's surface. The shoreline is visible in the distance, creating a layered effect with the land and water. Silhouetted trees and vegetation frame the right side of the image, adding depth and a natural border. The sky is ablaze with warm, reddish-orange hues, fading into deeper shades of orange and brown as it ascends. The overall effect is peaceful and serene.",
